.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, tea, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person drinking milk##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | hot-chocolate | tea | mirinda  | milk |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

