.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, hip-hop
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bluemaster, cain, prince
1. the fan country is not the cain-smoker##6
2. the vegafina-smoker and the fan blues have different parity positions##9
3. the bluemaster-smoker and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
4. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the fan classical is not the bluemaster-smoker##6
7. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fan blues##1
9. the prince-smoker is not the fan hip-hop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | country | hip-hop  | classical |
| Pet           | bluemaster   | vegafina     | cain | prince      |

