4. the american and the architect have the same parity positions##9
5. the photographer and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the nurse##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
8. the designer is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | designer | nurse | architect | photographer |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

