.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, singing, woodworking
4 different games are played: go, chess, backgammon, domino
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person playing go and the person playing chess##7
2. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person playing go##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person playing domino have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | chess     | backgammon     | domino     | go    |

