.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, white, coral, mauve
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the person who likes mauve is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the person who likes coral is not to the left of the person who likes mauve##8
4. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
5. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
8. the person who likes brown is the colombian##1
9. the person who likes mauve and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | white   | mauve    | coral | brown    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

